===Etymology===
From ''phaeo'' (brown) + [[-phyta]]

===Proper noun===
'''Phaeophyta'''

#{{botany}}: A [[botanical name]] for a [[taxon]] within [[kingdom]] [[Protista]] (or [[Chromista]]) that includes the [[brown alga]]e. The taxon is traditionally given the [[rank]] of a [[division]].

